                                    "content": "<p>Use the <b>Projected stock</b> button to display a graphical representation for the projected stock. This button is available from the following functions:</p><ul><li><b>Item</b>: From the <b>Sites</b> tab, open the <b>Edit</b> panel and go to the <b>General information</b> tab, <b>Stock</b> section.</li><li><b>Item-site</b>: Go to the <b>General information</b> tab, <b>Stock</b> section.</li><li><b>Sales order</b>: From a sales order line open the <b>Edit</b> panel and go to the <b>Quantities</b> tab, <b>Stock</b> section.</li></ul>",
